      "title": "Miraculous chicken in Yali",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A chicken with four legs has been hatched in a house in Achuveli-Kalanai area.",
        "Maharaja Gauri, a woman of the family, is engaged in poultry farming. He brings chicken farming as a way of life.",
        "Six chicks were hatched in his house, one of which was found with four legs."
